## 4. üè∑Ô∏è Standardized Field Values & Emojis

Use these standard values for consistency. Emojis provide quick visual cues.

### Statuses (`status:` field)

*   `‚ö™ Blocked`: üöß Cannot proceed (explain why in body).
*   `üü° To Do`: üì• Ready to be started.
*   `üîµ In Progress`: üèóÔ∏è Actively being worked on (human).
*   `ü§ñ Generating`: ‚ú® AI actively generating code/content.
