## 5. üìù Markdown Body Conventions

Use the body for human-readable details and collaboration.

*   **Title:** Optionally repeat the `title` from YAML as a top-level heading (`#`).
*   **Description (`## Description ‚úçÔ∏è`):** Clearly explain the *what* and *why* of the task. Provide background context.
*   **Acceptance Criteria (`## Acceptance Criteria ‚úÖ`):** **CRUCIAL.** Use Markdown checklists (`- [ ]`). Each item should be specific, measurable, achievable, relevant, and testable (SMART-ish).
