*   `# << CONCISE RESEARCH QUESTION >>`: Replace with the research title/question.
*   `## Description ‚úçÔ∏è`: Detail the research question, why it's needed, scope, and timebox (if any).
*   `## Acceptance Criteria (Definition of Done) ‚úÖ`: Define what constitutes a completed investigation (e.g., report generated, recommendation made).
