*   `## Findings / Results üìä`: Document the findings, comparisons, PoC results, etc.
*   `## Recommendation / Conclusion üí°`: State the final answer/recommendation with justification.
*   `## AI Prompt Log ü§ñ (Optional)`: Alternative space for logging AI interactions.
*   `## Review Notes üëÄ (For Reviewer)`: Space for feedback on the research.
